biography: Matthias Peussner has studied applied system science at the Osnabrück University, Germany. He worked several years as a software developer. Now he is working as scientist for ROSEN Technology & Research Center GmbH in Lingen, Germany. He has special interest in doing data science, developing machine learning models (deep learning) and creating software prototypes using Python.
